parts.text:
```json
{
"application": "obsproc",
"software": [
"grib_util",
"netcdf",
"bufr_dump",
"intel",
"craype",
"cray-mpich",
"cray-pals",
"cfp",
"prepobs"
],
"resource_requirements": {
"walltime": "0:30:00",
"queue": "dev",
"account": "OBSPROC-DEV",
"nodes": "1",
"cpus": "12",
"memory": "6gb",
"debug": "true"
},
"environment_variables": {
"envir": "prod",
"cyc": "%CC%",
"DESC": "%DESC%",
"JTYP": "%JTYP%",
"job": "${JTYP}_prep1_$cyc",
"jobid": "$job.$PBS_JOBID",
"PDY": "%PDY%",
"userROOT": "/lfs/h2/emc/obsproc/noscrub/$USER",
"obsproc_ver": "v1.1",
"obsproc_ver_pckg": "v1.1.2",
"prepobs_ver": "1.0.0",
"obsNET": "obsproc",
"PACKAGEROOTpara": "/lfs/h1/ops/para/packages",
"HOMEobsproc": "${userROOT}/install/obsproc-rel.v1.0.0",
"VERSION_FILE": "${HOMEobsproc}/versions/run.ver",
"SENDECF": "NO",
"SENDSDM": "NO",
"SENDDBN": "NO",
"DATAROOT": "/lfs/h2/emc/stmp/${USER}",
"jlogfile": "/lfs/h2/emc/stmp/${USER}/${JTYP}.$PDY.jlogfile",
"COMIN_ROOT": "/lfs/h2/emc/stmp/$USER/CRON/${DESC}/com",
"COMOUT_ROOT": "/lfs/h2/emc/stmp/$USER/CRON/${DESC}/com",
"DEBUG_LEVEL": "3",
"KEEPDATA": "YES",
"LOUD": "ON"
},
"commands": [
"module load grib_util/${grib_util_ver}",
"module load netcdf/${netcdf_ver}",
"module load bufr_dump/${bufr_dump_ver}",
"module load intel/${intel_ver}",
"module load craype/${craype_ver}",
"module load cray-mpich/${cray_mpich_ver}",
"module load cray-pals/${cray_pals_ver}",
"module load cfp/${cfp_ver}",
"module load prepobs/${prepobs_ver}",
"$HOMEobsproc/jobs/JOBSPROC_CDAS_PREP1"
]
}
```
